 air.&amp;nbsp; Mushroom mycelium thrives in fresh, circulating air.&amp;nbsp; If you have good circulation in your room, you don't need a fan.&amp;nbsp; If not, get one.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>12222034</next>\n<prev>12221934</prev>\n<first>12221309</first>\n<last>12224831</last>\n<when>1268891857</when>\n<utime>03/18/10 08:57 AM</utime>\n</post>"}